{"tid":1174361,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Gordon哥哥60天激減60磅　蕭徽勇公開蔬果汁斷食減肥法四大心得","createTime":"2019-05-27T20:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T05:53:52.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7f47369e596733655a27f8409e562c0791a71987","tid":1174361,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T20:29:20.000Z","msg":"曾主持兒童節目的TVB演員Gordon哥哥蕭徽勇，因為以蔬果汁斷食法於60天內激減60磅而受注意。近日，蕭徽勇更在facebook以過來人的身份分享蔬果汁斷食法食秘訣，鼓勵大家一起減肥。<br />\n蕭徽勇的體重最高峯時曾一度達300磅，他其後以蔬果汁斷食法，於60天內從248.6磅減至189.1磅，成功激減60磅。現時，趕拍《降魔的2.0》與《唐人街》的他，工作忙碌更加瘦，現在體重為168.7磅。<br />\n他以蔬果汁斷食法減肥，且於facebook專頁「復瘦者聯盟」拍片分享減肥心得，當中指出4大重點。<br />\n<br />\n1. 榨汁機<br />\n減肥者需要一部榨汁機，且提醒大家榨汁機和攪拌機是有分別的，因為經榨汁機所榨出來的蔬果汁是沒有渣滓的。<br />\n<br />\n2. 電子磅<br />\n蕭徽勇提示大家每天早上也需要上磅，觀察體重上的變化，從而得知自己減肥的進度。他建議大家可以將電子磅連接至手機應用程式上，方便隨時作參考。<br />\n<br />\n3. 連續60天<br />\n蔬果汁斷食法需要揀選連續60天進行，期間不能有任何一天停止，不可讓自己隨便找籍口。<br />\n<br />\n4. 無比決心<br />\n減肥很需要堅毅不屈的精神及無比的決心，方可走向成功，若然中途放棄了，便會前功盡廢。<br />\n<br />\n蔬果汁斷食法需要令腸胃得以休息，並可按照個人喜好以多種不同的蔬果配搭，製作出適合自己口味的蔬果汁。<br />\n<br />\n但Gordon提醒打算開始60天蔬果汁斷食前，可以先嘗試3日或5日。此外，開始斷食前一個星期要食吃得清淡，特別是盡量少吃肉，讓身體適應。<br />\n蔬菜汁含有草青味，也並非人人能夠接受，不過若然加入過多的水果作調味則會令果糖過多，並會引致肥胖，因而建議製作蔬果汁時，至少7成以上的食材為蔬菜。<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2355000/2359751/gordon_thumb_20190527_ch_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2355000%2F2359751%2Fgordon_thumb_20190527_ch_1024.jpg&h=04d9a0b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2355000/2359751/Gordon2019_4547_63_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2355000%2F2359751%2FGordon2019_4547_63_1024.jpg&h=a1501ea4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2355000/2359751/Gordon_1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2355000%2F2359751%2FGordon_1_1024.jpg&h=2ef4576e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2355000/2359751/Gordon20190527_654_73_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2355000%2F2359751%2FGordon20190527_654_73_1024.jpg&h=6c6be1b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8ccb46929b9b53563869b1aebdf33070aa5d148","tid":1174361,"uid":60699,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T20:32:53.000Z","msg":"個人閪 點減都無用"},{"pid":"325eca941e1366ae1764b8eed87fac9d1e3fbe53","tid":1174361,"uid":152123,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T20:38:34.000Z","msg":"肥佬變虧佬 帶咩意思"},{"pid":"939b1860b7b5d293dee2f713d66cfce611720c09","tid":1174361,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"325eca941e1366ae1764b8eed87fac9d1e3fbe53","tid":1174361,"uid":152123,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T20:38:34.000Z","msg":"肥佬變虧佬 帶咩意思"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T20:38:45.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"76e7fad49715078e93fa8e749fd6d77496739ee5","tid":1174361,"uid":88967,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T20:47:04.000Z","msg":"好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af24ab701d6ec50bb4472c9d4ab99b9659474173","tid":1174361,"uid":88967,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T20:47:41.000Z","msg":"瘦咗好似變咗樣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a822aaabd13d0b21bbaab1ab3cc9027a149ab434","tid":1174361,"uid":280,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T20:56:51.000Z","msg":"佢無工開就斷食得到.... <br />\n咁樣減邊健康....<br />\n篇文之前都睇過啦⋯⋯又攞出來講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown